{"tid":1312072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立係唯一既出路","createTime":"2019-07-13T12:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T19:35:09.000Z","uid":48259,"like":311,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"4ccd8bd5a4b46ec0a81d7d1c22e0ef013fd75437","tid":1312072,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"魯迅先生曾於1927 年在《無聲的中國》一文中寫道：&ldquo;中國人的性情總是喜歡調和、折中的，譬如你說，這屋子太暗，說在這裡開一個天窗，大家一定是不允許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開天窗了。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，可行與否，不解釋多了<br />\n之前好多巴打都出post講過<br />\n<br />\n我只希望大家可以幫手做多d文宣<br />\n或盡力輸出「香港獨立」既思想比大眾<br />\n只有當大部分人既終極訴求變成「香港獨立」<br />\n港共先有機會退而求其次回應我地其他訴求"},{"pid":"561a5100ab1077af1872b502b8c9443b17754a3c","tid":1312072,"uid":48259,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:19:53.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n香港獨立 香港獨立！"},{"pid":"e737407468a05866c153c4d16d1861a4a3082f20","tid":1312072,"uid":48259,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n香港獨立係唯一既出路"},{"pid":"dacbb10274cb82eaa7f42b943f790bc71ee398c4","tid":1312072,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:26:47.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe06853d06fa57a8feba710428573646305457d","tid":1312072,"uid":122709,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:29:13.000Z","msg":"香港獨立係必然之事<br />\n大家必須年年講 月月講 日日講<br />\n令香港新一代明白！"},{"pid":"de90c011a59f8b848d72497f57f623c40f48031b","tid":1312072,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2807451f14f29adc8477da00de40de209707aef3","tid":1312072,"uid":48259,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"而家既政府同黑警係擺撚到明唔係服務市民，佢地一日唔瓦解，香港係唔會康復！"},{"pid":"14b678d3f64f1cfbd2574a322cad088143647e06","tid":1312072,"uid":192971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13